'''第七合组军团'''（{{lang-en|Legio VII Gemina}}）<ref>Adkins,Lesley Adkins,Roy A.（1998）.''Handbook to Life in Ancient Rome''.Oxford University Press,USA.ISBN 9780195123326.</ref>[[古罗马|古罗马]][[军队|军队]]建制名称。由[[四帝之年|四帝之年]]时期的[[加爾巴|加爾巴]]于公元69年建立，该军团曾参加[[罗马帝国|罗马帝国]]对[[日耳曼尼亚|日耳曼尼亚]]的相关战争并发挥作用，<ref>Booking, ''N. D.'' pt. ii. pp. 1026, ''seq.''; Marquardt's ''Becker, Röm. Alterthum'', vol. iii. pt. 2, p. 354; Georg Friedrich Grotefend, in Pauly's Realencyklopädie, ''s. v.'' Legio.</ref>至公元4[[世纪|世纪]]末仍于历史著述中得到反映，<ref name="es">{{cite book |last=Rabanal Alonso |first=Manuel Abilio (coord.) |date=1999 |title=''La Historia de León, Vol. 1: Prehistoria y Edad Antigua'' |trans_title= |url=http://dialnet.unirioja.es/servlet/libro?codigo=515838 |language=es |location= |page=192 |publisher=Universidad de León |isbn=84-7719-817-9 |accessdate=2013-11-18 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203012236/http://dialnet.unirioja.es/servlet/libro?codigo=515838 |dead-url=no }}</ref>具有重要地影响与积极意义。
